snippet.title: I Taught Bootcamp: Everyone can Learn How to Code
snippet.description:
I wanted to share a few insights that I have regarding my experience teaching a bootcamp.  Overall, I think everyone can learn how to code if they put in the work and time. We'll have a live discussion on some of the important things about bootcamp students.

To support the channel:
Basic Training Course:
https://www.letsbuildthatapp.com/basic-training
